```

## Data Conventions

- Raw data in `data/raw/` is immutable — never overwrite
- Processed data goes in `data/processed/`
- Document data sources and schemas in this file or `data/README.md`

## Code Conventions

- Extract reusable logic from notebooks into `src/`
- Type hints on all functions
- Use pandas vectorized operations, avoid iterating rows
- Set `random_state=42` for all stochastic operations
- Log experiment parameters and metrics

